                    >
                </p>
                <p
                    class="uppercase text-blackColor font-medium dark:text-blackColor-dark"
                >
                Maktabs
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div>
                <img
                    src="https://via.placeholder.com/50"
                    alt="icon"
                    class="mx-auto"
                />
            </div>
            <div>
                <p
                    class="text-2xl font-bold font-hind text-blackColor dark:text-blackColor-dark"
                >
                    <span data-countup-number="400">400</span><span>+</span>
                </p>
                <p
                    class="uppercase text-blackColor font-medium dark:text-blackColor-dark"
                >
                Students Enrolled
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div>
                <img
                    src="https://via.placeholder.com/50"
                    alt="icon"
                    class="mx-auto"
                />
            </div>
            <div>
                <p
                    class="text-2xl font-bold font-hind text-blackColor dark:text-blackColor-dark"
                >
                    <span data-countup-number="1600 ">1600 </span><span
                        >+</span
                    >
                </p>
                <p
                    class="uppercase text-blackColor font-medium dark:text-blackColor-dark"
                >
                    Beneficiaries 
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Item 4 -->
        

        <!-- Repeat similar structure for Items 3 to 7 -->
    </div>

    <!--section 2 -->

    <!--section video -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-16">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden pb-[40%]">
            <iframe
                class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/rKE-aUoKWhE?si=Hix0Wt-am77ezPpB"
                title="YouTube video player"
                frameborder="0"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
                allowfullscreen
            >
            </iframe>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- -->
    

   
    <!--section 3 -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="row">
            <p
                class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-10 sm:mt-20"
            >
            Providing Quality Education
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
            <span class="text-grey font-bold">Our Maktab Project</span>, provides well-rounded, balanced Islamic education to orphans and children from low-income households, creating better futures through knowledge and learning. We strongly believe that the best form of education is that which balances worldly matters with religious and spiritual growth, which is why we designed our <span class="text-grey font-bold">Maktab project</span> to focus on both aspects of education. <br><br>Our school curriculum includes secular and Islamic subjects such as English, Maths, Urdu, Tajweed, Fiqh, Hadith, reading, and writing taught under the supervision of qualified Qaris. The purpose of our Maktabs is to support deprived students who cannot afford to study due to financial constraints. Your support ensures we can provide consistent, quality education, sharing the Qur’an, raising literacy rates, attainment and keeping children safe from exploitation.
            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <RestoringLives ReStroingLives={Restoring} />
    
    <!--section 5  -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="row">
            <p
                class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-maroon font-bold mt-10 sm:mt-20"
            >
            How does Al-Wahab Foundation use my donation?
            </p>
            <p
                class="mt-5 sm:mt-7 text-grey text-base sm:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
            >
            We believe that education is the key to breaking the cycle of poverty. Your donations can count as Sadaqah Jariyah for the long-term benefit they will bring to each child and their family.<br><br>We use your donation to enrol students in our Maktabs who would otherwise remain deprived of any Islamic education due to their families’ circumstances. We give these children the tools they need to build a positive future for themselves and to become advocates for Islamic education in their communities. <br><br>From hot meals to achievement awards, visits from <a href="#" class="text-maroon hover:text-customBeige font-bold ">Mufti Abdul Wahab</a> and Eid gifts, your donation helps to care for each student. Thanks to your Maktab support, we have been able to help 1,600 pupils so far due to your generous donations.<br><br>Donate today and your generosity will provide essential teaching resources, books, equipment and qualified staff, creating a stable, nurturing Islamic environment for children living in disadvantaged communities.

            </p>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--section 4 -->
   
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-10 sm:mt-12">
            <a
                href="#"
                class="bg-maroon hover:bg-customBeige text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 sm:px-8 rounded-full uppercase text-sm sm:text-base"
            >
                SUPPORT NOW
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--section step -->
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-1">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div
                class="bg-maroon flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 pb-6 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            >
                <svg
                    class="-mt-4"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="60"
                    height="60"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-pound-sterling mb-4"
                >
                    <path d="M18 7c0-5.333-8-5.333-8 0"></path>
                    <path d="M10 7v14"></path>
                    <path d="M6 21h12"></path>
                    <path d="M6 13h10"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold py-2 mt-3">Step 1</p>
                <p class="text-center font-semibold text-base">
                    You select maktab project and make a donation on our website.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div
                class="bg-customBeige flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-dark rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            >
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="60"
                    height="60"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-arrow-right-left mb-4"
                >
                    <path d="m16 3 4 4-4 4"></path>
                    <path d="M20 7H4"></path>
                    <path d="m8 21-4-4 4-4"></path>
                    <path d="M4 17h16"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Step 2</p>
                <p class="text-center font-semibold text-base">
                    Your donation is collected and goes towards maintaining and running our Maktab facility.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div
                class="bg-maroon flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 text-white rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            >
                <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="60"
                    height="60"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-wrench mb-4"
                >
                    <path
                        d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"
                    ></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Step 3</p>
                <p class="text-center font-semibold text-base">
                    We assess the progress of each child through annual examinations. We also hold a Khatam-ul-Quran graduation ceremony to acknowledge the children’s achievements.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div
                class="bg-customBeige flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 pb-6 text-dark rounded-lg shadow-lg"
            >
                <svg
                    class="duration-300 hover:stroke-maroon -mt-3"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="60"
                    height="60"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="lucide lucide-notepad-text mb-4"
                >
                    <path d="M8 2v4"></path>
                    <path d="M12 2v4"></path>
                    <path d="M16 2v4"></path>
                    <rect width="16" height="18" x="4" y="4" rx="2"></rect>
                    <path d="M8 10h6"></path>
                    <path d="M8 14h8"></path>
                    <path d="M8 18h5"></path>
                </svg>
                <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 mt-4">Step 4</p>
                <p class="text-center font-semibold text-base">
                    Children receive gifts from our team for the completion of their Quran.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--section 6-->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <p class="text-grey font-bold text-3xl text-center py-4">
                See other Project
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <Otherproject SeeOtherProjects={otherproject} />
</Layout>
